name: Living in The Cage
description:
We'll all be fine with the association of this bird cage picture and Jurassic Park's movie scenes. But what about the resemblance of it to invade and conquer and everything in between with science? Is it me, or is it also in nature that irony and beauty walk hand in hand?

Shot on Canon EOS 5/Kodak Ektar 100 | C41 Process | Noritsu Scan | 3602 × 2397px
